text: John Rogers (born 7 May 1943) is an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class and one List A matches for New South Wales between 1968/69 and 1969/70. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: John Rogers (cricketer, born 1943)
